outputStrategy

Class BasicBatch

  • java.lang.Object
    • framework.Implementation
      • outputStrategy.BasicBatch
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OutputStrategyInterface, ComponentReferences

    public class BasicBatch
extends Implementation
implements OutputStrategyInterface
    Basic implementation class of component OutputStrategy.

    This class implements a batch output strategy.

    It collects messages until an certain number of messages is collected.

    Author:
    Karl-Peter Fuchs
